    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Good palacement according to others tier 3 colleges",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Huge college campus , Many foods options in canteen , with deversified food prices and tastes, Ample Seating Options available in canteen.",
          "name": "Aman gudekar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classroom are huge with huge Seating Capacity, Smart Projector Teaching, Manual board is also there, Cleanliness, Availability of Student lift and wheel chair accessibility options as well.",
          "name": "Aman gudekar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Qualified Teachers, proactive measures of teaching, All are Masters in their Respective teaching Styles and some are even Doctorates in their respective fields.",
          "name": "Aman gudekar",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "COLLEGE CANTEEN IS AFFORDABLE AS IT HAS VARIETY OF OPTIONS IN CHEAP PRICES TO EAT EVERYDAY THOUGHT ISNT THE BEST BUT THE QUANTITY OF FOOD IS GOOD",
          "name": "Asaid shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty is pretty nice and the students were amazed after seeing the physics lab.",
          "name": "Mujtaba Sayed",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Most of the facilities are helpful and there are nice classroom though infrastructure is not modern but educomp is there in every classroom, there air conditioned laboratory, boys common room with a basic equipment gym and some indoor games",
          "name": "Mohammad Ozair Obaid Khan",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Faculty and staff members are very friendly and are very co-operative not only at the time of admission but at other times too they speak with politeness and kindness.",
          "name": "Review Rebel",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Non supportive faculty, they always try to harder your work",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "Assignment submission problem, they will make you ro beg for the submission",
          "name": "Review Ranger",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "INFRASTRUCTURE THE COLLEGE LOOKS GOOD FROM OUTSIDE AND IS PRETTY WELL MAINTAINED BUT THE CLASSROOMS ARE TOO OLD AND NEED RENOVATION THERE ARE NO ACS AND GOOD BENCHES",
          "name": "Asaid shaikh",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "They don't tell exam dates before 1 month.",
          "name": "Mujtaba Sayed",
          "course_tag_name": "BE"
        },
        {
          "text": "College are equipment are too old . Every machine is damaged are not working properly",
